{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1274517_translations":{"at":1774726984226,"data":{"id":1274517,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Erinn Westbrook is an American actress, singer, dancer and model. She is known for portraying Bree in Glee, Gabby Richards in the MTV series Awkward, and Magnolia Barnard in the Netflix series Insatiable. From 2021-2023, she starred as Tabitha Tate in The CW series Riverdale.","name":"Erinn Westbrook","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"Erinn Veronica Westbrook是一位美国女演员、歌手、舞者和模特。她因在《欢乐合唱团》中扮演Cheerios队长而闻名，Bree在MTV系列剧《Awkward》中扮演Matty的女朋友，以及斯坦福网球明星Gabby Richards。她还出演了Netflix电视剧《贪得无厌》，饰演Magnolia Barnard。","name":"艾琳·威斯布魯克","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"艾琳·威斯布魯克 是一位美國女演員、歌手、舞者和模特。她因在《歡樂合唱團》中扮演 Cheerios 隊長而聞名，Bree 在 MTV 系列劇《Awkward》中扮演 Matty 的女朋友，以及斯坦福網球明星 Gabby Richards。她還出演了 Netflix 電視劇《貪得無厭》，飾演 Magnolia Barnard。","name":"艾琳·威斯布魯克","primary":false}}]}},"person_1976642_translations":{"at":1774726985286,"data":{"id":1976642,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Mukkadas Kurban, known better as Dai Si for short, is an actress of Uyghur descent. She made her acting debut in the 2017 television drama “Eternal Love.” Mukkadas graduated from the Central Academy of Drama. She speaks four languages: Uyghur, Mandarin, English, and Russian.","name":"Dai Si","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"代斯，1991年8月14日出生于新疆乌鲁木齐，中国内地影视女演员，毕业于中央戏剧学院。\n\n2014年，出演个人首部古装探案剧《通天狄仁杰》，从而正式进入演艺圈。2015年，主演青春励志剧《我和胡杨的约定》。2016年2月，在古装玄幻剧《三生三世十里桃花》中饰演胭脂；9月，出演古装仙侠剧《轩辕剑之汉之云》。2017年3月，在古装言情剧《烈火如歌》中饰演刀冽香；7月，主演推理悬疑电影《生死语者·秦明》 。2018年，主演军旅剧《反恐特战队之天狼》。","name":"代斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Đại Tư","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"代斯","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"대사","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дай Сы","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"代斯，1991 年 8 月 14 日出生於新疆烏魯木齊，中國內地影視女演員，畢業於中央戲劇學院。\n\n2014 年，出演個人首部古裝探案劇《通天狄仁傑》，從而正式進入演藝圈。2015 年，主演青春勵志劇《我和胡楊的約定》。2016 年 2 月，在古裝玄幻劇《三生三世十裏桃花》中飾演胭脂；9 月，出演古裝仙俠劇《軒轅劍之漢之雲》。2017 年 3 月，在古裝言情劇《烈火如歌》中飾演刀冽香；7 月，主演推理懸疑電影《生死語者·秦明》 。2018 年，主演軍旅劇《反恐特戰隊之天狼》。","name":"代斯","primary":false}}]}},"person_209196_translations":{"at":1774726986063,"data":{"id":209196,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Annette Ngozi Ilonzeh is a Nigerian-American actress, known for her starring role as Emily Foster on NBC's Chicago Fire. From 2010 to 2011, she played Maya Ward on the ABC daytime soap opera General Hospital, and starred as Kate Prince in the short-lived ABC reboot of Charlie's Angels. She later had a recurring roles on shows such as Arrow, Drop Dead Diva and Empire.","name":"Annie Ilonzeh","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Annie Ilonzeh ist eine US-amerikanische Schauspielerin, die in Deutschland durch die Wiederauflage der Fernsehserie Drei Engel für Charlie bekannt geworden ist. Sie wurde dabei als erste der drei Hauptdarstellerinnen besetzt. In den USA war sie zuvor bereits durch die Serie General Hospital populär geworden, in der sie 2010 und 2011 die Figur Maya Ward spielte.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"Annette Ngozi Ilonzeh 是一位尼日利亚裔美国女演员，因在 NBC 的《芝加哥之火》中饰演艾米丽·福斯特而闻名。从 2010 年到 2011 年，她在 ABC 日间肥皂剧《综合医院》中饰演玛雅·沃德，并在 ABC 短暂重启的《查理的天使》中饰演凯特·普林斯。她后来在 Arrow、Drop Dead Diva 和 Empire 等节目中反复出演角色。","name":"安妮·伊隆泽","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"Annette Ngozi Ilonzeh 是一位奈及利亞裔美國女演員，因在 NBC 的《芝加哥之火》中飾演艾米麗·福斯特而聞名。從 2010 年到 2011 年，她在 ABC 日間肥皂劇《綜合醫院》中飾演瑪雅·沃德，並在 ABC 短暫重啟的《查理的天使》中飾演凱特·普林斯。她後來在 Arrow、Drop Dead Diva 和 Empire 等節目中反覆出演角色。","name":"安妮·伊隆澤","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Энни Илонзе","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"アニー・イロンゼ","primary":false}}]}},"movie_452964_credits":{"at":1774727020041,"data":{"id":452964,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1313985,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Barbie Castro","original_name":"Barbie Castro","popularity":0.9847,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":7,"character":"Sandra Cruz Durro","credit_id":"58f766ae9251415df800c16f","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":41687,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Patrick Muldoon","original_name":"Patrick Muldoon","popularity":1.3959,"profile_path":"/nuqKElpRossYTwh9BIymHLA5G6e.jpg","cast_id":8,"character":"Charles Durro","credit_id":"58f766b5c3a36841d300c0e0","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1763622,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Kate Mansi","original_name":"Kate Mansi","popularity":0.813,"profile_path":"/iJiK7jC3WdVnRVvoiDw8d3giJnV.jpg","cast_id":9,"character":"Krystal Kellers","credit_id":"5